text: Dharmendra Singh Senthwar is an Indian politician. He is a Member of the Uttar Pradesh Legislative Council since 11 August 2022. He is a member of the Bharatiya Janata Party. He is from Gorakhpur district, Uttar Pradesh, India. == Political career == He has been the Regional President of the Bharatiya Janata Party in Gorakhpur since 2022. ==References== Category:Politics of India
title: Dharmendra Singh Senthwar
